00:11:05.570 --> 00:11:09.980
And then, I got in, I did the American Music
Awards for her, same thing.

00:11:09.980 --> 00:11:14.660
And then, I got in the Oscars that year, which
was the year Paula Abdul choreographed it.

00:11:14.660 --> 00:11:18.520
Yes, I'm a Paula Abdul dancer.

00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:19.520
[laughter]

00:11:19.520 --> 00:11:25.630
